text: Wittenbra is a location on the now closed Gwabegar railway line in north- western New South Wales, Australia. A station was located there between 1923 and 1960.Wittenbra station NSWrail.net, accessed 9 April 2010. ==References== Category:Disused regional railway stations in New South Wales Category:Railway stations in Australia opened in 1923 Category:Railway stations closed in 1960
